start with jvm opts

-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote

http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/management/jconsole.html

to allow jvisualvm to attach

jvisualvm

http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/tools/share/jvisualvm.html

to load logging.properties start with the following jvm opts

-Djava.util.logging.config.file=logging.properties
